div.div:
Every 'SamplePeriod' seconds, the Update()-function is called, which
updates all available metrics using various other packages.
First, utilization metrics are updated using BPF and NVME sensor packages, and aggregated to containers, VMs and nodes.
Then, all energy metrics are read, and a delta to the last update cycle is calculated. Using the attribution model, these energy metrics are attributed to containers, VMs and nodes based on the process' utilization.

The "power" interface abstracts sensor implementation.
Behinde the "power" interface are sensors packages for:
- accelerators (NVML, but also others)
